<HEADLINE> Lipinski Shares Skating Secrets </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	TROY, Mich. (AP) -- Tara Lipinski knows a thing or two about  
figure skating and doesn't mind sharing her secrets. 
</P>
<P>
	The Olympic gold medalist helped with a session on jumps Sunday  
at a skating clinic attended by about 300 skaters of all ages. 
</P>
<P>
	``There're tons of kids (here),'' said Ms. Lipinski, who turns  
17 on June 10. ``Without them, I wouldn't be able to do what I 
love. For them to be able to meet me makes me feel happy that 
they're happy about it.'' 
</P>
<P>
	Ms. Lipinski turned pro after winning the gold in Japan.  
  	   	
</P>
