	Some were trampled to death, while others suffocated. Forty-two  
of the dead were girls. 
</P>
<P>
	``There was such a huge crowd. I was carried away by it when it  
rushed to the underpass,'' said Vitaly Milentyev, 19. ``I was 
lucky. I managed to get out of the crowd literally by going between 
the legs of other people.'' 
</P>
